## Code Example

```javascript
function aggregateDeltas(deltas) {
  // de-duplicate by user/app+event, then sample
  const seen = new Set();
  const out = [];
  for (const d of deltas) {
    const key = d.userId + '|' + d.appId + '|' + d.eventId;
    if (!seen.has(key)) {
      seen.add(key);
      if (Math.random() < d.sampleRate) out.push(d.aggregate);
    }
  }
  return out;
}
```

